commit.message:
tests: Add NVMe controller type checks

This one was missing in the tests. Also, reorder the checks
so that it matches order of the struct elements.

tests: Add NVMe persistent discovery controller tests

Just a simple connect to a well-known discovery NQN.

btrfs: make btrfs subvolume listing consistent

Depending on the given mountpoint listing subvolumes returns different
pathnames. The pathnames are returned sort of relative to the provided
mountpoint. For example listing with `/` as mountpoint can return:

['root', 'home', 'home/foo', 'foo']

While giving `/home` it returns:

['root', 'home', 'root/foo', 'foo']

This gives issues for Cockpit as we want to give users a consistent
listing of their subvolumes and UDisks always uses the first MountPoint
to look up the subvolumes so Cockpit would either have to figure out how
that is relative to the given MountPoint or show inconsistent
subvolumes.

commit.message:
tests: Fix removing custom LVM devices file

shutil.rmtree works only with directories, not with files.

tests: Ignore LVM devices file for non-LVM tests

We are creating LVM setups for some FS and DM tests manually and
we don't want to deal witht he LVM devices file in these cases.

tests: Manually remove removed PVs from LVM devices file

pvremove doesn't remove the PV from the devices file so after
running our tests suite we have hundreds of invalid entries in the
file.

commit.message:
tests: introduce setup_test_device helper function

Reduce some code duplication by introducing a test class helper function
which set's up a test device optionally with a different size.

This also seems to speed up the tests to 64 seconds from 74 seconds.

tests: split multi device tests into a new testcase class

The BtrfsTestCase always makes two iscsi devices while they aren't
always needed, there are quite some IO costs in bringing these devices
up. Before and after timings:

Ran 24 tests in 113.267s
Ran 24 tests in 76.454s
